{"tid":2333619,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"[台港連合演出]識咗班人佢地搞咗個網上音樂會，仲會代你寄聖誕卡畀台灣朋友","createTime":"2020-12-20T14:42:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T14:21:04.000Z","uid":264620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bfe926c2a209a4dd9dce57faa54dd11aa30f2a2a","tid":2333619,"uid":264620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T14:42:55.000Z","msg":"睇返佢地同啲新嘅香港獨立歌手都幾frd幾support咁<br />\n<br />\n我覺得最有心思係買飛可以代你寄聖誕卡畀人，如果寄台灣仲會係當地發件<br />\n即係你唔使驚香港寄嘢畀台灣[s]手足[/s朋友]時會有地址畀人跟到～有心有心～<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UKwvLNx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUKwvLNx.jpg&h=07747a75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/2860410164194087\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F2860410164194087&d=10CjJG2g6dwwFxaVJa0PIQvpIPIfgcH1aomtamkqoQA%3D&h=d0e1e41a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/2860410164194087</a><br />\n<br />\n以下係佢地嘅post：<br />\n辦這次《Our Season's Greeting Live》港台音樂會動機原自之前的閒談：<br />\n「又開始限聚令了，12月大部分的工作和節目都取消了。」<br />\n「似乎2020年就是如此完結吧？唉～」<br />\n「不如辦個音樂會吧，至少親手將2020年如何完結握在自己手裡！」<br />\n我們在想，最好的完結就是如常一樣大家聚在一起，互相祝福。<br />\n然後在這一年，我們身邊有很多朋友都走到台灣，相信是因為這個地方有著和香港相似的氣氛。<br />\n所以我們構思了港台兩地一起合演的線上音樂會，希望可以和大家聚在一起。<br />\n由決定到公佈只有短短幾天，感謝每個伙伴由表演單位到的幫忙。<br />\n現在，我們希望得到你們的支持：<br />\n1)拍攝祝賀短片，讓我們在直播中播出（時間有限，先到先播）<br />\n2)購票支持-- 每張門票我們都會送上一張節日名信片，會代你填好寄到收件人地址，不限香港台灣。<br />\n相信我們可以在互相的祝福下走進2021年。<br />\n購票:<br />\nKKTIX: <a href=\"https://daymakercreatives.kktix.cc/events/1226greetings\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdaymakercreatives.kktix.cc%2Fevents%2F1226greetings&d=10CjJG2g6dwwFxaVJa0PIQvpIPIfgcH1aomtamkqoQA%3D&h=2b285a96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://daymakercreatives.kktix.cc/events/1226greetings</a><br />\nTICKCATS: <a href=\"https://tickcats.co/ticket/ourseasonsgreetings\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftickcats.co%2Fticket%2Fourseasonsgreetings&d=10CjJG2g6dwwFxaVJa0PIQvpIPIfgcH1aomtamkqoQA%3D&h=dd278350\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tickcats.co/ticket/ourseasonsgreetings</a><br />\n<br />\n－－－－<br />\n<br />\n見佢地咁有心，幫手出post share 下，各位有興趣記得買飛支持下～<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0359d7ca6829ec2609e8b17a09e3a7a9c771f2c","tid":2333619,"uid":264620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T07:44:30.000Z","msg":"push～"},{"pid":"28abb77bf8f77ef102a32400e15873b01b5c53cd","tid":2333619,"uid":264620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T08:57:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3a356b4448512398f0c7e62c4f4a6a72232b5e1c","tid":2333619,"uid":264620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:33:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f0e98e249b0bca68991389161989aa517513d95f","tid":2333619,"uid":264620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T02:57:31.000Z","msg":"再push"},{"pid":"4b105977df31c485753f058f97b1bb3f3a0bbf5e","tid":2333619,"uid":264620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T08:12:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"814a3c612191b726f3a6de895ce4b7b7be469d6a","tid":2333619,"uid":264620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T14:21:04.000Z","msg":"聽晚就係，希望大家支持～<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/meK6eBB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmeK6eBB.jpg&h=50799163&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}